ers!", "short_description": "Band Space - Demo is the lite version of the upcoming online co-op VR rhythm game. You can play drum sets, guitar, keyboard, or bass on shining stages. Team up with a band, make friends, and become a rock star! Try it now for Free!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Cover-Portrait-1008x1440.png", "id": "3242314529236062", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75520131_3242314532569395_4127143000398014575_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uRCIuZ9vmbsQ7kNvgGSaspf&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD0U6QtaT4TM20AtTVnKTRf4MR_OffQylscsgFXeaeECw&oe=67010B45"}, {"file_name": "Hero-Cover-3000x900_New.png", "id": "2718068125034139", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75234369_2718068128367472_2174447360667117750_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=G3GZPHS-kfIQ7kNvgEddKKH&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBy54h6ZWqLcLltA-YTo481UFBFa0rPK6VlKG9ojEKXMQ&oe=6701297C"}, {"file_name": "Cover-Square-1440x1440.png", "id": "1599677630597013", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569443_1599677633930346_8775915673430657994_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ot2J94k_IHEQ7kNvgEGTDiK&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDR1KQHjNqei3QsRdonVtbgDzX_NuhYBwGToNhFGjXxlA&oe=67013733"}, {"file_name": "Bandspace_Meta_Logo_3697x1440.png", "id": "1149661772909261", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_1149661776242594_3873384865056879737_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=De_lEGiNXmUQ7kNvgGKxyfZ&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDOkFKzYdxMUbUxbJI9Jxr9r1fXkP9s4ZoEy1DEarDpmA&oe=67013B7A"}, {"file_name": "Icon512x512.png", "id": "907329050642509", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t6